Qatelghiinkuk Amaankuk

Qatelghii tapgham qukaani mallungluni ayveghmeng neghumaluku sunanguq taana amaa.
Kaalluni amaam qatelghii pimakanga, "Whangallu neqaghlanga.
Igatapigtunga."
"Legan neghi.
Uglaghllagtuq.
Whangangingaghma naangnnaanghitaqa."
Llaaghanwha amaallu neghumalghii.
Iwemgaqun kepsughlutek neghlutek tapgham kelutanganilngughmun uusneghwaaghmun mayuumalghiik.
Qaygeghsamek qatelghiim amaa pimakanga, "Whani yeqay meghnaaliltung.
Wiin qavaaltung."
Llaaghanwha amaa aanghumalghii.

Tawani uusneghwaaghem qaayngani ingaghquusimalghiik.
Qatelghii qavaghpenani teghhumaamalghii.
Amaa qavaghyan whaa tungunghaqasan qatelghii nekevluni tamaani qemgughtimalghii ayveghem kuyapegaaneng.
Qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii nuuvulluki amaam paapgakun qilleghsimakangi.

Enkaam amaa taghsaamakaanga.
Qatelghiim pimakanga, "Anguyaget sughuget whaa kaasaghtuungestaamiikung.
Uusneghwaaghmun mayiigaqut.
Whanga qimagnaqunga.
Elpek saaqsin?"
Amaa qaviinamaatkun nekefqaghlluni pangalegyalghiimi kelutmun uka tunganganeng kavleggalek.
Naqam paapga aqniimaghmi.
Amaa sumeghtaghaamalghii, "Seghleghhalekkaannaqaatnga anguyaget.
Tuqunnaqaatnga.
Awitwuwaqlu papemkun kiitegtaatnga.
Sangami paapka aqnighaqa?"
Amaa iwemgaqun qevuulluni qimakaq tuqunnayukangatni.
Qimaguqestaghngaaghmi kinguminilnguq kavlek almesiqngiinaghyagu saama pekapigsami amaa sumeghtaghaamalghii, "Qaywaam tuqulanga."
Aghuliighutkelluku uteghmun qiivyalghiimi sughumeng esghaanneghituq.
Katam taawa paapgakun qilleghlluteng qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii.
Amaa pimalghii, "Uguminaghnaghhalek qatelghiipenaaq pekaghtepigtaanga.
Kergam taawa esghaqaghtekumken unguvallequten."

Qatelghiim kiiwek kaallukek akimun ayuqelghiik maligsimakek iwemgam esnamun.
Tawani esnami tepameng neghemsuglimi taglaamalghii esnam kelutanganun.
Pengughaghhaghmun kaalluni tawani qavaghnaqsami iyegni nusugraghlukek saaghwmikun llilukek qavaamalghii.
Taagken amaam ugumiyagulluku qatelghii tamaghhaani ivaghtaayaqenni.
Qenwatlu naalkeqaghsimakanga.
Qatelghii qavaghaqeftuq enngaatall umuluku naqam saaghwani iyek.
Amaamtaghsaghpenaan iiskekqatelghiimtutmaghtaalukek qageghqughlukek unisimakanga.
Kingunganeng amaam qatelghiim iwemgaqun qavagni nusuglukek taghtughyami iyegni tugunaqsaqegni aviituk.
Katamnaalkumakekqageghqughlleraaghinaak.
Qatelghii ayaaluni paneghluni tuqumalghii.

Qamagtuq.
